{"tid":848602,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚午餐 香煎澳洲穀飼帶骨豬扒 配 加勒比海莎莎 萍果燒汁","createTime":"2018-10-05T05:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T10:11:40.000Z","uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bc024c8542f0a8278a51a92442f7f6fc167f5bed","tid":848602,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/130449_6ea2f5c1357577349b8c32a690defc1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F130449_6ea2f5c1357577349b8c32a690defc1b.png&h=69fb4c81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e82bbd20d76b06d3d72fe410b04a133815a6381","tid":848602,"uid":113064,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n有緣仲會見到連登飲食台<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅硬台柱</strong></span><br />\n香港飲食評論<del><strong>打手</strong></del>界<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>超級巨星</strong></span></span><br />\n聲稱<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中立非 _ _ (百搭<del>亂填</del>)</strong></span></span>嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">慘過番印度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n百里香 觀塘駿業街67號熟食市場1樓44號<br />\n路線：港鐵觀塘站A2出口 步行約6分鐘<br />\n營業時間：一至五11:00-16:30；六11:00-16:00<br />\n外賣熱線：67082851<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">資料由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原創者</span>那吾克儉提供</span>"},{"pid":"1c7b201c32037f4ec797960ab6d5c14885e0f6a3","tid":848602,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"中非打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588feeaee821a1b80416646bec130588ea336ce4","tid":848602,"u